data.name: SelectInstructionsLabel.Text
data.value: Select a version from the list below to change your WTDE version, and the updater will download it. To return to the most recent version, click "Revert to Current Version" above. This feature requires WTDE updater version 2.1.2 or later.

data.name: OutOfDateWarningLabel.Text
data.value:
IMPORTANT NOTE ABOUT INSTALLING OLDER VERSIONS:
If you run into issues with these older versions of GHWT: Definitive Edition, asking for help in the WTDE help line, you will be asked to update your build to the latest version of the mod.
WE DO NOT PROVIDE SUPPORT FOR OLD VERSIONS OF WTDE. RUN THESE VERSIONS AT YOUR OWN RISK.
